            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the field closely related to carbon neutralization such as CO2 large-scale capture, utilization and storage, clean energy development and utilization, ecological management and the like, and particularly relates to a method and system for CO2 storage, water collection, heat collection and hydrogen production application. The method is a technical application centered on CO2 geological sequestration displacement of stratum salt water and utilization of renewable energy sources or other energy sources available according to local conditions for photolysis or electrolysis of salt water for hydrogen production. The system comprises a CO2 capturing and transporting module, a CO2 geological storage and saline water layer displacement water taking module, a water resource hydrogen production and heat collection and other valuable resource development and extraction module and a resource comprehensive utilization module. The CO2 storage capacity can be remarkably improved, the problem of efficient large-scale disposal and utilization of the produced salt water is effectively solved, a renewable energy source + CCUS + geothermal energy + hydrogen energy + resource development coupling scheme is achieved, high comprehensive benefits and long industrial chain potential are achieved, CCUS economy is expected to be improved, and large-scale commercial application of CCUS is promoted."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于CO2大规模捕集利用与封存、清洁能源开发利用以及生态治理等碳中和密切相关的领域，具体涉及一种CO2封存采水采热制氢应用的方法与系统，是一种以利用CO2地质封存驱替地层咸水并利用可再生能源或其他因地制宜可利用的能源光解或电解咸水制氢为中心的技术应用；所述系统包括CO2捕集与运输模块、CO2地质封存与咸水层驱替取水模块、水资源制氢采热及其他有价资源开发提取模块、资源综合利用模块；本发明可显著提高CO2封存容量，有效解决采出咸水的高效大规模处置利用问题，实现可再生能源+CCUS+地热能+氢能+资源开发耦合方案，有较强综合效益与较长产业链潜力，可望提高CCUS经济性，推动其大规模商用落地。"
                }
            ]
